    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行启动股票回购和股权置换计划以提振市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/pboc-starts-share-buyback-equity-swap-programs-to-boost-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行已启动专项再贷款安排，供上市公司和大股东回购股票，此举是此前宣布的广泛刺激计划的一部分，旨在刺激资本市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/pboc-starts-share-buyback-equity-swap-programs-to-boost-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国 GDP 增长放缓，凸显刺激措施的紧迫性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-18/china-s-gdp-growth-slows-highlighting-stimulus-urgency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国第三季度国内生产总值同比增长 4.6%。这低于第二季度 4.7% 的增长，是自 2023 年 3 月以来的最低增速。澳新银行首席大中华区经济学家杨伟雄讨论了最新数据对世界第二大经济体的健康状况和政府政策的影响。他在“彭博：中国秀”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-18/china-s-gdp-growth-slows-highlighting-stimulus-urgency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家统计局：中国经济正在进行“结构转型”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-18/china-economy-making-structural-transformation-nbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家统计局副局长盛来运在新闻发布会上表示，中国经济正在经历“结构转型”时期。（来源：APTN）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-18/china-economy-making-structural-transformation-nbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 03:02:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管中国努力复苏，房价仍持续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/china-home-price-slump-drags-on-despite-revival-efforts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国9月份房价下跌速度与上月几乎相同，这表明国家稳定房地产行业的努力可能还不够。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/china-home-price-slump-drags-on-despite-revival-efforts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 01:41:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国加强卖空打击力度 一家对冲基金遭起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/former-staff-of-australian-hedge-fund-regal-indicted-in-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国监管机构已起诉澳大利亚最大的对冲基金之一从事卖空交易，这表明首尔方面已将对此类交易的打击范围扩大至整个金融行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/former-staff-of-australian-hedge-fund-regal-indicted-in-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 00:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格首次突破 2,700 美元，延续创纪录的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/gold-hovers-near-record-as-mideast-tensions-spark-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东冲突升级和美国大选竞争激烈的担忧，投资者纷纷涌向避险资产，金价首次突破每盎司 2,700 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/gold-hovers-near-record-as-mideast-tensions-spark-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 23:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯领导人死亡后，焦点转向中东，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-18</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 死后，人们关注中东局势的发展，油价在五个交易日内首次上涨，随后小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-18</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 23:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
